   "source": [
    "File Handling:\n",
    "it allow us to create, read, write, update and delete files.\n",
    "it is used to store data permanently.\n",
    "\n",
    "the built-in function is open() to work with files\n",
    "common modes:\n",
    "1. 'r' - read\n",
    "2. 'w' - write\n",
    "3. 'a' - append\n",
    "4. 'b' - binary\n",
    "5. 't' - text\n",
    "6. 'rb' - read binary \n",
    "7. 'wt' - write text \n",
    "\n",
    "File path:\n",
    "    1. Relative path- file name\n",
    "    2. Absolute path- directories(complete loc) + file name "
   ]
